## Container.has() method

Return a boolean indicating if a given key exists.

Signature:

```typescript
has(key: string): boolean;
```

Decorators:

`@bind`

## Parameters

| Parameter | Type   | Description |
| --------- | ------ | ----------- |
| key       | string |             |

Returns:

boolean

## Example

```js
container.has("my-key");
// true if container.repository['my-key'] exists
```
